Should these functions still reset the values on the spins?

If these were removed because we don't want the widgets to trigger new signals, we could wrap the `setValue` calls with the [blockSignals](http://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qobject.html#blockSignals) function, for example:

~~~
void JointForceControl::Reset()
{
  this->dataPtr->forceSpin->blockSignals(true);
  this->dataPtr->forceSpin->setValue(0.0);
  this->dataPtr->forceSpin->blockSignals(false);
}
~~~
